message.body: Ok! Tonight is the big night! Anyone who is available and/ or interested in helping move stall stuff out if the shed rows tonight, and back in tomorrow night, just show up. We will have pizza and beer and any other requests food/drink for any helpers! :) see ya tonight if you can make it! :) tell me what you want to eat, I will get it!! thanks!!!! Tan
Probably won't be done til about 8-8:30 ish then eating
I figured Caitlin, just figured you'd like to know what's going on
:( ugh so sorry! Hope he's better soon ! I hope I don't get sick, I hear more n more people getting it lately!
Ok! No sheds moving today! Problem with the shed people. New shed mover doing it tomorrow, FYI, ugh! Sorry people! Thanks for your patience! :)
Oh good! Maybe we won't be in the dark tomorrow and it's perfect weather for field board :)
